w TV 從網上看到我在元朗出現，便剎有介事打電話來向我查詢，問我為何在元朗出現，還與白衣人拍照，可會與元朗白衣人打黑衣人事件有關？我說絕對沒有任何關係，我只是晚飯後經過，有很多市民還認識我，他們很認同我為港敢言發聲支持警察維持治安，要求跟我和我拍照，我亦樂於接受。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於記者的深宵查問，我反而向記者查問他們可有查詢泛民議員總是掩護黑衣暴徒，每當嚴重暴力衝突事件發生後，不單只沒有譴責，更明言不割𥱊，明顯地包疪暴力罪行。記者雖說會去調查，但是由六月十二日至今發生了多次暴力事件，傳媒至今仍是冷處理而沒有報導泛民的不是，那是否極不尋常呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114759088616955/posts/2367685086657666?s=753094347&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114759088616955%2Fposts%2F2367685086657666%3Fs%3D753094347%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXch5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=406be22f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114759088616955/posts/2367685086657666?s=753094347&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"仆你個街啦屌！"},{"pid":"4c95bd204fb55ef0583c2523c8a34c4e78bb857a","tid":1343332,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"幾時搵何老妖算帳"},{"pid":"e8d3f24f6f4bfad463030c9b10b368c7842c6404","tid":1343332,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"大家緊記 揸緊五大訴求 唔好俾鄉黑spin到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1337952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1337952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"126105aa9e15a21251dcc3ea8d8ad66349188e29","tid":1343332,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:55:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005593bd40d6d93bf3007dc3f5e9c0afff32725f","tid":1343332,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49ece92da8130aebfe35b4b480e8b60a4b6c2cd","tid":1343332,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=