s code 以顏色區分是否繼續可行？<br />\n如果著 smart casual 恤衫返工裝，<br />\n人人都係打工仔，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>人人都係 water</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n到時打，打打工仔，打平民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三、</span></span>除 TVB 有免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道外，<br />\nViuTV 同奇妙電視應該要同樣加開免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道，<br />\n本身兩台已有班底，只須加開頻道即可<br />\n甚至可考慮<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港首創本地 24 小時英語新聞頻道</span></ins></strong><br />\nRTHK 31 亦要加強推廣自身頻道<br />\n<br />\n同溫層講，大家都識得睇其他新聞，<br />\n但須知道好多酒樓、食肆冇嘢好播，咪播 TVB 新聞，<br />\n上年紀一輩只識打開對眼就睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四、</span></span>同樣唔可以忽視就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>境外酒店電視落地</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n大家打開酒店電視，睇香港嘅頻道，只會搵到 TVB，得 TVB 落到地，<br />\n呢方面要大家諗諗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>（外地人士第一觀感）</ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6ebefffad3c89d0ae1bb9d7fad18a60c24a33af5","tid":1343332,"uid":217004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:14:53.000Z","msg":"何閪妖幾時先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e66ca28609d5e1faa074c436ad4f923c4ff5ca","tid":1343332,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味"},{"pid":"9370ed711c04cb1b056b55b512dba9f0b2d96196","tid":1343332,"uid":73219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"有暴力嘅地方就有何君妖"},{"pid":"7fa939187168746e7f91f57407808dc84ee18987","tid":1343332,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:17:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1153007779734360064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1153007779734360064&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXch5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=28982422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F